Text: Please please keep on seeding this amazing collection of books.It is the most exhaustive collection I've ever seen.I can't think of a single book which is not in this collection.Simply great.Thanks TiGORin but keep on seeding please.

Dear TiGORiN,
I had to thank you once again now that I have downloaded quite a few books from your amazing collection.I can't express my gratitude in words but just want to tell you--You'll always be in my prayers.Please keep on seeding this phenomenal collection for as long as you can.God bless you.
Dont forget to thank the other seeders too.  I've been seeding for about 2 years myself.  Gotts keep it alive.
